The Martian review

   abookandacuppa:

     image

     The Martian by Andy Weir

     Rating: ★★★★★

     I watched the movie a few years ago, and thoroughly enjoyed it, so I
     assumed I would enjoy the book just as much. And I was right! This
     book was absolutely incredible. I was on the edge of my seat the
